rule-11-13-a.test_description: A one story single zone building has service water heating systems. The service hot water system has use but with units OTHER.
rule-11-13-a.expected_raised_message_includes: This building has service water heating loads. Confirm that service water heating energy consumption is calculated explicitly based upon the volume of service water heating required and the entering makeup water and leaving service water heating temperatures

standard.rule_description: Service water-heating energy consumption shall be calculated explicitly based upon the volume of service water heating required and the entering makeup water and the leaving service water-heating temperatures. Entering water temperatures shall be estimated based upon the location. Leaving temperatures shall be based upon the end-use requirements.
